352
00:17:48.209 --> 00:17:50.309
Second is Takuma so it's six.

353
00:17:50.309 --> 00:17:52.109
Fourth is Ayumi, so it's two.

354
00:17:52.109 --> 00:17:54.509
Fifth is me and it's one.

355
00:17:54.509 --> 00:17:56.309
If we read this in order it goes.

356
00:17:56.309 --> 00:18:01.909
Four, five, three, six, two, one.

357
00:18:01.909 --> 00:18:04.509
Yo-ko-sa-mu-ni-i?

358
00:18:04.509 --> 00:18:06.809
It's mumbo-jumbo, isn't it?

359
00:18:06.809 --> 00:18:09.909
Maybe it's not the word chain game?

360
00:18:09.909 --> 00:18:11.409
It has to be!

361
00:18:11.409 --> 00:18:14.909
Because the word chain fits in too well to be a coincidence!

